    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>GODS &amp; GORE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款以希腊神话为背景的Roguelike塔防游戏。选择你的神明，收集神话生物，保卫你的城市。每轮扩展城市，增强你的防御、力量和连击，以抵御越来越强大的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300870/extras/47e374134f215582566508ce64e344e6.poster.avif?t=1772045117\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300870/extras/47e374134f215582566508ce64e344e6.webm?t=1772045117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300870/extras/47e374134f215582566508ce64e344e6.mp4?t=1772045117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>指挥</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集在多次游戏间持续存在的神话生物。宙斯的金鹰、牛头怪等等。提升它们的等级，让它们在每次尝试中变得更强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300870/extras/45f8a0c367838c5acb92faa87e7aba99.poster.avif?t=1772045117\" aria-label=\"宙斯的金鹰攻击敌人\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300870/extras/45f8a0c367838c5acb92faa87e7aba99.webm?t=1772045117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300870/extras/45f8a0c367838c5acb92faa87e7aba99.mp4?t=1772045117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>建造</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部署你的防御工事。位置至关重要：创造瓶颈、叠加升级，将你的城市变成堡垒。每波敌人来袭时，选择强大的建筑卡牌。塔楼、兵营、城墙、增益建筑——一张一张卡牌构建你的策略。每局游戏都不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300870/extras/50316810fbc3af38d18b118a04f557e3.poster.avif?t=1772045117\" aria-label=\"玩家选择一张卡牌来放置建筑并扩展城市\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300870/extras/50316810fbc3af38d18b118a04f557e3.webm?t=1772045117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300870/extras/50316810fbc3af38d18b118a04f557e3.mp4?t=1772045117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>防御</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies come in waves - barbarians, berserkers, brutes, and legendary giant enemies. Each wave hits harder so you must be strategic as you upgrade your towers, send warriors to fight, spend gold, and command your creatures. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300870/extras/5a536096027415cf84af9694b5186f14.poster.avif?t=1772045117\" aria-label=\"大量敌人涌向城市，被防御塔和闪电击倒\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300870/extras/5a536096027415cf84af9694b5186f14.webm?t=1772045117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4300870/extras/5a536096027415cf84af9694b5186f14.mp4?t=1772045117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于卡牌的建造系统，拥有无限叠加升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跨游戏的生物收集和力量成长</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多位神明，各具独特能力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断升级的波次，直到你倒下</p></li></ul>",
